{"tid":2224584,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蓬佩奧促梵蒂岡譴責中國侵犯宗教自由　未獲教廷正面回應","createTime":"2020-09-30T15:18:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T05:50:44.000Z","uid":39464,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a21572b1e3d989b9eef070940868e07d7c77a3b2","tid":2224584,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T15:18:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://stream.881903.com/public/26c0694dc90ff42e69b9e1bf949c4b8f/2020/09/d8ec21f1af04b761e0d24685803784f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstream.881903.com%2Fpublic%2F26c0694dc90ff42e69b9e1bf949c4b8f%2F2020%2F09%2Fd8ec21f1af04b761e0d24685803784f0.jpg&h=4ecf4e6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到訪梵蒂岡的美國國務卿蓬佩奧，出席美國大使館主辦的研討會，批評中國是世界上，攻擊宗教自由最嚴重的國家，因中共視自己為最終的道德權威，並對自身缺乏民主合法性感到恐懼，因而日以繼夜撲滅自由之燈，打擊所有宗教。他敦促教廷加入美國，譴責中國侵犯宗教自由，在捍衛人權的鬥爭中站在最前線。 <br />\n<br />\n教廷為準備延續中梵主教任命臨時協議作出辯護，強調有關協議不涉及政治或中梵建交。出席研討會的梵蒂岡外長加拉格爾發言，未有提及中國，只是批評西方有人鼓吹性別意識，侵犯宗教自由。他其後向記者表示，蓬佩奧此行不獲教宗方濟各接見，其中一個原因是因為臨近美國大選。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2359710\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2359710&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyiWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=d579e569\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2359710</a>"},{"pid":"cec96f0a523a19b743191cedbcb97a71b64f9125","tid":2224584,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T15:21:06.000Z","msg":"D教徒出黎講2句"},{"pid":"d5fbeec8867f6ecd06b11bd71b1c5108a2ca8cb7","tid":2224584,"uid":305358,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T15:23:05.000Z","msg":"宗教只不過係一盤生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6348eaa8c76e9ccde1c3c90a4c24e41164901328","tid":2224584,"uid":310461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T00:58:14.